#### 6.9 Stack recommandée (résumé)
```
Metrics:  Prometheus + VictoriaMetrics + Grafana
Logs:     Loki + Fluent Bit + OpenSearch
Traces:   OpenTelemetry Collector + Grafana Tempo
Network:  LibreNMS + Zabbix + Blackbox Exporter
Security: Wazuh (SIEM + EDR)
Alerting: Alertmanager + Grafana OnCall
FinOps:   OpenCost + Infracost
```

